*"Potrazi*me najbolji restoran u gradu." (Look for me the best restaurant in town.)

*"Potrazili*smo dobar motel za nas boravak." (We found a good motel for our stay.)

*"Molimo vas da *potrazite* mesto gde se može kupiti hrana." (Please find a place where food can be bought.)

*"Oni su *potrazili* posao u inostranstvu." (They looked for a job abroad.)

*"Njegov prijatelj je *potrazio* da mu pomogne." (His friend looked for him to help.)

*"Molimo vas da *potrazite* pomoć u slučaju problema." (Please look for help in case of problems.)